show.title: The Blind Billionaire
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/uZgPry
show.description:
After a crash leaves her brother in a coma, Shambhavi sells all she has for surgery funds. A blind billionaire offers to pay if she marries him and becomes his eyes. What’s waiting for her now? Will this be the start of something new or does this man have a hidden agenda?
Attaching reference images too.
